00055 bool
00056 NIVissimSingleTypeParser_Laengenverteilungsdefinition::parse(std::istream& from) {
00057     // id
00058     std::string id;
00059     from >> id;
00060     // list of points
00061     PositionVector points;
00062     std::string tag;
00063     do {
00064         tag = readEndSecure(from);
00065         if (tag != "DATAEND") {
00066             SUMOReal p1 = TplConvert<char>::_2SUMOReal(tag.c_str());
00067             from >> tag;
00068             SUMOReal p2 = TplConvert<char>::_2SUMOReal(tag.c_str());
00069             points.push_back(Position(p1, p2));
00070         }
00071     } while (tag != "DATAEND");
00072     NBDistribution::dictionary("length",
00073                                id, new Distribution_Points(id, points));
00074     return true;
00075 }
